'''馬克-阿倫·"麥斯"·格拉度'''（{{lang-fr|'''Marc-Alain "Max" Gradel'''}}，{{bd|1987年|11月30日|catIdx=Gradel, Max}}）是一名[[科特迪瓦|科特迪瓦]]足球員，司職[[中場#翼鋒|翼鋒]]，出身[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]青訓系統，現效力[[法甲|法甲]]球會[[圖盧茲足球會|圖盧茲]]。

==生涯==

===莱斯特城===
格拉度出身自[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]青訓，他於2007/08球季獲得了[[球衣號碼|球衣號碼]]。2007年5月5日，他和七名球員與莱斯特城簽訂了他自己首份職業合約，其中包括{{Link-en|艾力·奧希岩保|Eric Odhiambo}}、[[安迪·金|安迪·金]]和{{Link-en|卡爾·彭特尼|Carl Pentney}}<ref name="Young Stars Make The Grade">{{en}}{{cite web |title=Young Stars Make The Grade |url=http://www.lcfc.com/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1021228,00.html |work=LCFC.co.uk |publisher=Leicester City F.C. |date=2007-05-05 |accessdate=2009-03-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218091507/http://www.lcfc.com/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10274~1021228%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-02-18 }}</ref>。

===般尼茅夫===
8月6日，領隊{{Link-en|馬田·艾倫|Martin Allen}}表明將格拉度和[[康拉德·羅根|康拉德·羅根]]列入來季可供借用的名單中<ref name="Duo Available">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Duo Available| url=http://www.lcfc.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1085809,00.html| work=LCFC.co.uk| publisher=Leicester City F.C.| date=2007-08-06| accessdate=2007-08-06}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。8月9日，格拉度被外借至[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]，為期一個月<ref name="Gradel On The Move">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Gradel On The Move| url=http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1088370,00.html| work=LCFC.co.uk| publisher=Leicester City F.C.| date=2007-08-09| accessdate=2007-08-09| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://archive.is/20070616180251/http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1088370,00.html| archivedate=2007-06-16}}</ref>，後來球會於8月31日當天延長了借用期<ref name="Gradel Loan Extended">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Gradel Loan Extended| url=http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1103641,00.html| work=LCFC.co.uk| publisher=Leicester City F.C.| date=2007-08-31| accessdate=2007-08-31| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080107061928/http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10274~1103641%2C00.html| archivedate=2008-01-07}}</ref>。不幸的是，他並未能代表般尼茅夫上陣太多賽事，因為他的母親在10月初逝世。最終，時任般尼茅夫領隊{{Link-en|奇雲·邦德|Kevin Bond}}告訴格拉度，他可以自己決定哪時才返回[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]<ref name="Club 100% Behind Max">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Club 100% Behind Max| url=http://www.afcb.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10324~1130376,00.html| work=AFCB.co.uk| publisher=A.F.C. Bournemouth| date=2007-10-08| accessdate=2007-10-08| archive-date=2009-04-14| archive-url=https://archive.is/20090414021043/http://www.afcb.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10324~1130376,00.html| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。 

2008年1月3日，他提早重返李斯特城後，般尼茅夫表示希望再次借用格拉度<ref name="Cherries Rue Loan Departures">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Cherries Rue Loan Departures| url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_3019302,00.html| work=SkySports.com| publisher=British Sky Broadcasting| date=2008-01-03| accessdate=2008-01-03| archive-date=2008-01-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080106063148/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_3019302,00.html| dead-url=no}}</ref> ，最終他在1月11日再度被外借至般尼茅夫<ref name="Bournemouth re-sign Foxes' Gradel">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Bournemouth re-sign Foxes' Gradel| url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bournemouth/7183837.stm| work=BBC Sport| publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation| date=2008-01-11| accessdate=2008-01-11}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。2月6日，他在般尼茅夫的表現，使李斯特城與其簽訂了3年合約<ref name="Gradel Pens New Foxes Deal">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Gradel Pens New Foxes Deal| url=http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1233603,00.html| work=LCFC.co.uk| publisher=Leicester City F.C.| date=2008-02-06| accessdate=2008-02-06| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207093939/http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10274~1233603%2C00.html| archivedate=2008-02-07}}</ref>。

===重返莱斯特城===
2008年8月9日，他在[[獲加球場|獲加球場]]對[[米爾頓凱恩斯足球會|米爾頓凱恩斯]]的賽事中首次代表李斯特城於聯賽上陣，他並且交出助攻，協助球隊以2-0勝出<ref name="Leicester 2-0 MK Dons">{{en}}{{cite news| title = Leicester 2-0 MK Dons| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541043.stm| work = BBC Sport| publisher = British Broadcasting Corporation| date = 2008-08-09| accessdate = 2008-08-09| archive-date = 2017-08-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170827134339/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541043.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。8月14日，他與球隊簽訂新約，起碼效力至2012年<ref name="Gradel Extends City Stay">{{en}}{{Cite news| title=Gradel Extends City Stay| url=http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1365414,00.html| work=LCFC.co.uk| publisher=Leicester City F.C.| date=2008-08-14| accessdate=2008-08-14| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080904104354/http://www.lcfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10274~1365414%2C00.html| archivedate=2008-09-04}}</ref>。2009年1月14日，格拉度在[[英格蘭足總杯|足總杯]]對[[水晶宮足球會|水晶宮]]的賽事中攻入他加盟以來的首球，不過球隊最終以1-2落敗<ref name="Crystal Palace 2-1 Leicester">{{en}}{{cite news| title=Crystal Palace 2-1 Leicester| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7815358.stm| work=BBC Sport| publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation| date=2009-01-14| accessdate=2009-03-01| archive-date=2009-04-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417031138/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7815358.stm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月28日，在對米爾頓凱恩斯的賽事中，他於傷停時間的攻進了一球關鍵的[[自由球|自由球]]，協助球隊以2-2逼和對手，這同時亦是他的首個聯賽入球<ref name="MK Dons 2-2 Leicester">{{en}}{{cite news| title=MK Dons 2-2 Leicester| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7905733.stm| publisher=BBC Sport| date=2009-02-28| accessdate=2009-03-01| archive-date=2009-03-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301224905/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7905733.stm| dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月23日，他在對米爾頓凱恩斯的賽事中的入球，使他獲得李斯特城支持者球會獎項中的年度最佳進球<ref name="Trio honoured at awards">{{en}}{{cite news |title=Trio honoured at awards |url=http://www.lcfc.com/page/LatestNews/0,,10274~1634825,00.html |work=LCFC.co.uk |publisher=Leicester City F.C. |date=2009-04-23 |accessdate=2009-04-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218092142/http://www.lcfc.com/page/LatestNews/0%2C%2C10274~1634825%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-02-18 }}</ref>。格拉度當季代表李斯特城上陣了27場聯賽賽事，協助球隊贏得聯賽冠軍並升班[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]。

自李斯特城升班後，格拉度開始不受重用，僅上陣了一場[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]賽事。李斯特城在夏季轉會市場買入了{{Link-en|丹尼·尼基辛|Dany N'Guessan}}<ref>{{en}}{{cite news| title = Foxes sign N'Guessan from Lincoln| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8121040.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-06-26| accessdate = 2009-10-20| archive-date = 2009-07-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090708054819/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8121040.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>和{{Link-en|保羅·加歷查|Paul Gallagher (footballer)}}<ref>{{en}}{{cite news| title = Foxes sign Blackburn's Gallagher| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8213994.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-08-21| accessdate = 2009-10-20| archive-date = 2009-08-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090828012451/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8213994.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>後，格拉度並未能在2009/10球季上陣。

===外借列斯聯===
{{Quote box | width=30% | align=right | quote=他有很好的速度和不錯的素質。|source= <small>[[西蒙·加利臣|西蒙·加利臣]]<ref name="Gradel joins Leeds on loan deal"/></small> }}

2009年10月19日，他被外借至[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，為期一個月<ref name="Gradel joins Leeds on loan deal">{{en}}{{cite news| title = Gradel joins Leeds on loan deal| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8315905.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-10-20| accessdate = 2009-10-20| archive-date = 2009-10-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091024224342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8315905.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>，與此同時，他的前般尼茅夫隊友[[森·禾基斯|森·禾基斯]]亦於同日加盟<ref>{{en}}{{cite news| title = Leeds sign Wolves' Vokes on loan| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8315591.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-10-19| accessdate = 2009-10-20| archive-date = 2009-10-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091023085905/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8315591.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。他在對[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]的賽事進行至最後15分鐘時處子上陣，他凸出的表現使賽後他贏得了最佳球員獎<ref name="Leeds United   2 - 1   Norwich">{{en}}{{cite news| title = Leeds United   2 - 1   Norwich| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8306388.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-10-19| accessdate = 2009-10-20| archive-date = 2009-10-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091021080604/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8306388.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。首次借用期間4次後補上陣，表現獲得列斯聯領隊西蒙·加利臣滿意，希望延長借用到2010年1月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5669977,00.html |title=Grayson keen to keep Gradel |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-02 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2009-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091225073839/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5669977,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而他亦表示喜歡留在[[艾蘭路球場|艾蘭路球場]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5691285,00.html |title=Gradel wants Leeds stay |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-12 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2009-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091227004125/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5691285,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終獲李斯特城准許留效到2010年1月2日，但可在24小時通知後召回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5693141,00.html |title=Leeds retain Gradel |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-13 |accessdate=2009-12-17}}</ref></small>。11月24日主場迎戰[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:莱顿东方;zh-hk:奧連特}-]]，格拉度下半場後補上陣於89分鐘的入球絕殺對手<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8362924.stm |title=Leeds United 1-0 Leyton Orient |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-24 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2009-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126164230/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8362924.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。雖然主要擔任替補角色，但格拉度取得3次最佳球員獎，有傳列斯聯會在轉會窗重開時作出正式收購，但李斯特城回應格拉度為「非賣品」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5734493,00.html |title=Whites warned off Gradel bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-11-30 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2009-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091204055224/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5734493,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。12月30日，格拉度的外借期再延長至1月17日，即合共93日外借最長的期限<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5812540,00.html |title=Whites extend Gradel loan |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-12-30 |accessdate=2009-12-31 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310091229/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_5812540,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。借用期滿後格拉度返回李斯特城，但西蒙·加利臣隨即提高收購價再次求售<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5874249,00.html |title=Leeds up Gradel bid |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-20 |accessdate=2010-01-21 |archive-date=2010-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122161940/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12874_5874249,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，本季僅1次後補為李斯特城上陣的格拉度亦要求轉會，兩會達成轉會費協議，他前往[[艾蘭路球場|艾蘭路球場]]接受體測<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8474587.stm |title=Leeds United agree fee for Leicester City's Max Gradel |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-01-24 |accessdate=2010-01-25 |archive-date=2010-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100126105541/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8474587.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===列斯聯===
2010年1月25日，格拉度通過體測後，正式動筆簽約，為期兩年半<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5884490,00.html |title=Gradel seals Leeds switch |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-25 |accessdate=2010-01-26 |archive-date=2010-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100128082805/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5884490,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

